lead_paragraph: Jessica January scored 25 points and No. 18 DePaul remained unbeaten by holding off Western Kentucky 77-69 on Friday in the Gulf Coast Showcase.

headline.print_headline: January's 25 Gets No. 18 DePaul Past Western Kentucky, 77-69
